post_text:
On Saturday, October 26, 15 students from Springdale Jr-Sr High school attended the annual Kennywood Fright Night Show Choir event. The day was spent at McKeesport HS with students from 4-5 other schools learning music and dances to perform in the evening at Kennywood. Fun was had by all in spite of the rain! (Everyone was thoroughly soaked by the end of the performance of Thriller!)

Students who participated : Kaylee Bolar, Emmaleigh Flatt, Skyler Kowal, Rachel Hicks and Kaden Mizak (Grade 8);
Hailey Shondeck (Grade 9); Holly Hodil, Molly Hodil, Autumn Sprouse and Matthew Yungwirth (Grade 10);
Zack Conte, Bre Cummings, Emily Mattarochia, Jamie Tabaka, and Sonny Yungwirth (Grade 12)
#DynamoProud

